item.title: Compile Error [HELP!]
item.dc:creator: @Timister Timister
item.description:
@Timister wrote:

What JDK do you have?
Download Java ™ 2 Platform.

Go into Compile right click, click edit, Paste this in it:

@echo off title Compile and Server Runner "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac" *.java java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server pause

If that dont work… then IDK…

@echo off COLOR 0c title ___scape Compile "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe" server pause
